        "customfield_12520": "+*AC: 1 configure billing by multiple PO's*+\r\n\r\nAs a finance administrator, I want to setup client bills by multiple PO's, so that I bill according to client agreement\r\n\r\n*Give* that  a client needs to be billed by PO\r\n\r\n *And* only one PO can be billed in the same client invoice\r\n\r\n*When* the finance administrator configures the billing configuration\r\n\r\n*Then* the user must be able to specify that bills are generated by PO\r\n\r\n*And* the only one PO can be included in a single invoice\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n+*AC: 2 Billing items due for billing*+\r\n\r\nAs a finance administrator, I want to restrict invoicing by PO, so that bills without a PO number are not sent to clients\r\n\r\n*Given* that a client is setup to be billed by PO\r\n\r\n *And* only one PO can be billed in the same client invoice\r\n\r\n*When* the AR clerk adds items due for billing to a client invoice\r\n\r\n*Then* the items with different PO's must be added to different invoices\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n+*AC: 3 Adding items to a client invoice*+\r\n\r\nAs a finance administrator, I want to restrict invoicing by PO, so that bills without a PO number are not sent to clients\r\n\r\n*Given* that a client is setup to be billed by PO\r\n\r\n *And* only one PO can be billed in the same client invoice\r\n\r\n*When* the AR clerk adds items to a client invoice\r\n\r\n*Then* the AR clerk must only be able to add items with same PO number",
